  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0db4\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0d9a\u0dca \u0dbd\u0dd3\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca \u0db4\u0dc4\u0dbb \u0d9a\u0dd1 \u0db8\u0dd2\u0dad\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0dcf \u0daf\u0dd2\u0db1 4 \u0d9a\u0da7 \u0db4\u0dc3\u0dd4 \u0db8\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dba\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The friend who was hit with a betel nut died after 4 days",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to Homagama Headquarters Police, a person was beaten to death with a palm tree after an argument between two friends in front of a house in Pitipana Dham Mawatha area of \u200b\u200bHomagama.",
        "The police say that the deceased is a (40)-year-old man named Don Sumit Chandana of Matara, resident of Homagama, Pitipana South.",
        "It is said that these two people are friends and used to drink alcohol together every day.",
        "Accordingly, on the morning of the 13th, another person came in front of the house of the deceased and an argument took place between the two, and then it escalated into a fight.",
        "It is said that the person who was attacked endured the attack and spent four days drinking heavily as usual.",
        "In the meantime, on the morning of the 17th, the person who was assaulted collapsed at home and was admitted to the Homagama Basic Hospital, where he died while receiving treatment.",
        "Accordingly, according to a complaint filed by the deceased's sister to Homagama police regarding the incident, during the investigation, information was revealed that on the morning of the 13th, a friend of the deceased came and ran away after hitting him with a betel nut.",
        "Later, considering it a suspicious death, Nugegoda Division Crime Scene Investigation Agency officers and Homagama Magistrate arrived at the scene and started an on-site investigation.",
        "The Homagama Magistrate, who examined the place of the incident and the body, said that the body should be taken to the Kalubowila Teaching Hospital and a specialist doctor should conduct the post-mortem examination.",
        "Accordingly, the dead body was admitted to the Kalubowila Teaching Hospital and the post-mortem examination conducted there revealed that the cause of death was internal bleeding due to a blow to the groin area and broken bones.",
        "Accordingly, after it was revealed that the death was a murder by assault, the 27-year-old resident of Homagama, Pitipana, who carried out the assault, was arrested last (17) evening while hiding in a house.",
        "Later, the suspect is to be presented to the Homagama court along with Puwak Liya who did the assault.",
        "Under the direct supervision of Nugegoda Division Senior Superintendent of Police Mr. Chandana Liyanage and on the instructions of Assistant Superintendent of Police Mr. Pushpakumara, under the direction of Chief Inspector of Police Homagama Headquarters Mr. Thusitha Wickramaratne, the officers including Chief Inspector Kariyawasam of the Criminal Investigation Division are conducting further investigations."
      ],
